6.Given an integer n. Write a program to print the Right angle triangle. The length of the perpendicular and base is n.  
Platform : Geeks For Geeks
SOURCE CODE :class Solution {
    public void printPattern(int n) {
         for(int i=1;i<=n;i++){
         for(int j=1;j<=i;j++){
             if(i==1||i==n ||j==1||j==i)
               System.out.print("* ");
               else
                System.out.print("  ");
         }
     System.out.println();
    }
    }
}
